MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2009-0975. State ex rel. Skillas v. Indus. Comm.

Franklin App. No. 07AP-1064. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of *1467Appeals for Franklin County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

It is ordered by the court that the application for dismissal is granted. Accordingly, this cause is dismissed.
